				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I think you can do up to 10 connections to the server per second
<br />

<br />
1. add buddy
<br />
2. receive status
<br />
3. rem buddy
<br />
4. receive confirmation
<br />

<br />
so you can add/rem maybe 3 players per second
<br />

<br />
86,400 seconds in a day, so about 29,000 characters in a day
